    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior paint retains a nice gloss, though there are some minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable; while the seats show some light wear, there are no rips or significant stains. Mechanically, the car is solid and drives well, offering a dependable and pleasant experience for its next owner.",
