    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition, offering a functional and drivable option for someone who doesn't mind a bit of wear and tear. The engine and transmission are operational, though the car would benefit from a tune-up as there is some minor vibration at highway speeds. Visually, the exterior has several noticeable paint chips and a small door ding, while the interior shows clear signs of age, including some staining on the upholstery and wear on the steering wheel. It is a dependable choice for point-A to point-B travel, but please expect to invest in some minor repairs and cosmetic detailing to restore its overall appeal.",
      "price": 22500.0,
